        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/421/535",
        "text": [
          "٤٢١. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): كَفَاكَ مِنْ عَقْلِكَ مَا أَوْضَحَ لَكَ سَبِيلَ غَيِّكَ مِنْ رُشْدِكَ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "421. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: It is enough if your wisdom distinguishes for you the ways of going astray from those of guidance."
